Author: swirlturls
Text: i don't do it to be malicious. i dont just randomly have sweets and give them to fatten people up or something. but often if i am eating i dont like to finish the last bite. i will ask someone if they want it or i will throw it out. its more because i feel bad to waste lol. it's not an "omg i INSIST TAKE MY FOOD!!" it's a "bro imma throw this in the trash do u want it at all or"

Author: wild_banana_cookie
Text: I show food through love, so I will give sweets to people I know will eat it, but otherwise I will cook healthy if we are both sharing a meal.
